DOC.HEADLINE: 5 DEAD IN ALPS FALLS
DOC.TEXT: Four German climbers were killed Saturday in a fall_in the_Swiss Alps , police said , one day after the hiking death of a German woman . The climbers reportedly slipped as they left the summit of an 11 # 200-foot mountain in the central Alps . The 32-year-old German woman died when she lost her balance on a pass in Stechelberg .
